OL,3,CMinister accused of breaching human
OL,4,Crights law in teachers' pay dispute
OL,6,FShortly after ITV News shared the
OL,7,Fletter, one Jersey politician called
OL,8,Fthe approach "nasty and cowardly".
OL,10,FIn a social media post, Deputy Rob
OL,11,FWard added: "A disgraceful approach to
OL,12,Findustrial relations. Straight out of
OL,13,Fthe anti-Union playbook. Destroys
OL,14,Fprinciple of secret ballot. I call on
OL,15,Fthe vice chair SEB (States Employment
OL,16,FBoard) to withdraw this letter
OL,17,Fimmediately."
