OL,3,CMinister accused of breaching human
OL,4,Crights law in teachers' pay dispute
OL,6,FThe National Education Union (NEU) and
OL,7,Fthe National Association of Head
OL,8,FTeachers (NAHT) have also both
OL,9,Frequested the letter be rescinded.
OL,11,FIn a letter dated 30 January and
OL,12,Faddressed to Deputy Millar, the NEU
OL,13,Fwent further.
OL,15,FIt called her approach a breach of
OL,16,FArticle 11 of the European Convention
OL,17,Fof Human Rights, the freedom to join
OL,18,Ftrade unions and take part in peaceful
OL,19,Fprotests.
