OL,3,CMinister accused of breaching human
OL,4,Crights law in teachers' pay dispute
OL,6,FThe NEU added: "We do not accept the
OL,7,Fletter is lawful.
OL,9,F"We do not accept you can threaten to
OL,10,Fend the rights of our members to take
OL,11,Findustrial action while the dispute
OL,12,Fbetween the NEU and the States of
OL,13,FJersey continues.
OL,15,F"We further consider that your
OL,16,Fproposals would involve unlawful
OL,17,Fprocessing of our member's special
OL,18,Fcategory data that would deny their
OL,19,Fentitlement to confidentiality as
OL,20,Fregards their trade union membership."
