OL,6,FThe NEU however says it is still
OL,7,Fwilling to negotiate with Jersey's new
OL,8,Fgovernment and has called for urgent
OL,9,Ftalks to "re-establish good industrial
OL,10,Frelations".
OL,12,FCaryn Symoms, Senior Regional Officer
OL,13,Fat the NEU, added: "The change in the
OL,14,Fpolitical environment is positive.
OL,16,F"We have presented a new pay offer
OL,17,Fwhich we think is reasonable and we
OL,18,Fare hopeful that we will be able to
OL,19,Fget back round the table as soon as
OL,20,Fpossible and further those
OL,21,Fnegotiations."
