OL,6,FITV News understands Jersey's Chief
OL,7,FMinister, Deputy Lyndon Farnham, is
OL,8,Fnow leading on the issue.
OL,10,FIn response, he said: "There is a
OL,11,Fgenuine desire by this Government to
OL,12,Fresolve the current teachers' pay
OL,13,Fdispute and reset the workplace
OL,14,Frelationship so that we can move
OL,15,Fforward."
